    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 rounded-full mb-8 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-400 rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
          <span class="text-emerald-300 font-semibold text-sm">No upload • No tracking • WASM-powered</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-6" style="letter-spacing:-0.03em; line-height:1.08;">
          Your automations are a risk.<br />
          <span class="gradient-text">You just can’t see it yet.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-300 mb-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto font-medium leading-relaxed">
          One expired credential, one URL change, one person leaving — and your workflows quietly break.<br />
          Relay turns your Zapier export into a <span class="text-white font-black">Risk Audit</span> or a
          <span class="text-blue-300 font-black">Continuity Report</span> you can hand to a client, a team, or an auditor.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-10">
          <a href="/app.html#audit" class="px-8 py-4 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white text-lg font-black rounded-xl shadow-xl shadow-blue-500/30 transition-all hover:scale-[1.03] inline-flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
